strings.Value: "It's strange to remember how, as a child, I enjoyed all the bright dresses, bows and ruffles..."
"And I like them all so much! Too bad I don't often get a chance to dress up."
"I still love them, even now. What's wrong with that? A bird's bright feathers don't interfere with its talons, if it decides to use them."
